title: Select Windows in Emacs With Character Labels
tags: @zettel _method emacs doomemacs
roam-id: 42e2bc7b-e31e-43de-9657-6693634e3735
type: text/markdown

put the following into your config.el or init.el

``` elips
(setq aw-keys '(?j ?k ?l ?f ?a ?s ?h ?g ?d)) ;; select windows with chars instead of numbers
```
